Class TymeacPOAImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.rmi.PortableRemoteObject
      • com.tymeac.base.TymeacPOAImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TymeacInterface, java.rmi.Remote

    public final class TymeacPOAImpl
extends javax.rmi.PortableRemoteObject
implements TymeacInterface
    This class is identical to com.tymeac.base.TymeacIIOPImpl except that this class is for the Portable Object Adapter and requires rmic with the -poa option.
